c0000000
00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:03.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:06.630 --> 00:00:09.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE] You eighteen mages
passed the first test.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:10.430 --> 00:00:12.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well done,
I congratulate you all.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:13.930 --> 00:00:16.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know what people
whisper about me.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:16.520 --> 00:00:19.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The results of my previous
trials are intimidating,</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:19.270 --> 00:00:21.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and you've no doubt prepared
yourselves for the worst.</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:21.980 --> 00:00:24.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:24.190 --> 00:00:28.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please allow me to offer solace
and put your fears to rest.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:28.150 --> 00:00:30.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You won't face
the insurmountable today.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:31.320 --> 00:00:33.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My test
is actually quite simple.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:34.080 --> 00:00:36.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyone who wishes
to become a first-class mage</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:36.410 --> 00:00:38.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>should be able
to pass it with ease.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:38.370 --> 00:00:40.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:40.170 --> 00:00:44.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That said, I suggest you listen
closely to my instructions.</b></Default>

c0000014
00:02:17.970 --> 00:02:18.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:19.060 --> 00:02:22.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE] In order for you
to complete the second test...</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:22.520 --> 00:02:24.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you must conquer
this labyrinth,</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:24.140 --> 00:02:26.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>known as the Ruins
of the King's Tomb.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:28.070 --> 00:02:30.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To move on to the third trial,
you must reach</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:32.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the deepest level
of the dungeon.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:32.820 --> 00:02:34.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is the only requirement.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:35.740 --> 00:02:37.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am a pacifist...</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:37.490 --> 00:02:40.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I abhor fighting and conflict.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:40.160 --> 00:02:43.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Therefore, everyone who reaches
the bottom floor will pass.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:43.920 --> 00:02:45.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BLEI] Hold on.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:45.960 --> 00:02:48.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Many adventurers have attempted
to explore this dungeon,</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:48.960 --> 00:02:50.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but few have walked out.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:50.800 --> 00:02:53.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're sure you're not
planning to fail us all?</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:53.300 --> 00:02:54.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you want to be here?</b></Default>

c0000029
00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:55.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000030
00:02:55.970 --> 00:02:57.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE]
You are currently attempting</b></Default>

c0000031
00:02:57.470 --> 00:02:59.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to reach the pinnacle
of magehood.</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:00.470 --> 00:03:04.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>First-class mages can make
the impossible possible.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:04.480 --> 00:03:07.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why should it matter
who's entered this tomb before?</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:07.150 --> 00:03:09.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're here to gauge
your abilities.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:09.230 --> 00:03:10.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:10.610 --> 00:03:13.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm assuming that there must be
some definitive way of proving</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:13.530 --> 00:03:15.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that we reached
the bottom level.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:15.490 --> 00:03:17.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps there's a treasure
we're supposed</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:17.240 --> 00:03:18.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to return to you?</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:18.660 --> 00:03:21.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You won't need
to prove anything.</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:21.120 --> 00:03:24.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll descend to the depths
of the dungeon with you.</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:24.290 --> 00:03:26.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE] Though, naturally,
I'll offer no assistance.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:26.620 --> 00:03:28.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:28.250 --> 00:03:29.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One more thing.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:29.790 --> 00:03:32.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Each of you will take
a rescue bottle with you.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:32.380 --> 00:03:34.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:34.420 --> 00:03:37.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These were designed
by Lernen, a first-class mage.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:37.930 --> 00:03:39.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They hold escape golems.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:40.470 --> 00:03:43.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Break the glass
and it will grow to full power.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:43.100 --> 00:03:45.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At that point, it will
remove you from the dungeon.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:46.640 --> 00:03:49.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're still prototypes,
but they should be safe enough.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:49.860 --> 00:03:50.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be warned...</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:50.940 --> 00:03:53.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>using your golem
means you fail the test.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:53.480 --> 00:03:55.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I urge you to do so
if you can't continue</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:55.860 --> 00:03:57.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>due to injury or other hurdles.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:03:57.990 --> 00:04:01.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't want any mages with
promising futures dying here.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:01.830 --> 00:04:04.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, and this trial
has a time limit.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:04.330 --> 00:04:07.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The bottles will shatter
automatically at dawn tomorrow.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:04:07.660 --> 00:04:10.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll want to manage your
hours wisely as you explore.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:10.540 --> 00:04:12.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:12.540 --> 00:04:15.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With this in mind,
you're free to begin.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:15.260 --> 00:04:17.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:26.100 --> 00:04:28.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:36.190 --> 00:04:38.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's more
than one point of entry.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:38.490 --> 00:04:41.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I believe this was built
during the Unified Dynasty.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:42.070 --> 00:04:43.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] Dungeons from that era</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:43.160 --> 00:04:44.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>were constructed
with multiple entrances,</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:44.990 --> 00:04:47.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but each one leads
to the deepest level.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:48.080 --> 00:04:50.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Examining the various paths
inside might allow us</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:50.750 --> 00:04:53.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to better understand the
internal structure of the tomb.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:54.630 --> 00:04:56.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It'd be wise to work together.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:56.590 --> 00:04:59.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Surely you're not suggesting
that we help one another out?</b></Default>

c0000073
00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:02.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind howling]</b></Default>

c0000074
00:05:03.300 --> 00:05:04.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000075
00:05:04.760 --> 00:05:05.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
There's no reason for us</b></Default>

c0000076
00:05:05.930 --> 00:05:08.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to fight or face this alone.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:05:08.310 --> 00:05:10.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We would all benefit
from cooperation.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:05:10.980 --> 00:05:12.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footfall]</b></Default>

c0000079
00:05:12.100 --> 00:05:13.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is not happening.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:05:15.730 --> 00:05:17.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TON] Unlike the last test,
our companions</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:17.690 --> 00:05:20.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>don't have to survive
in order for us to pass.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:20.700 --> 00:05:22.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're under no obligation
to engage</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:22.240 --> 00:05:23.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>our fellow candidates.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:23.780 --> 00:05:26.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides,
you know your dungeons.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:26.160 --> 00:05:27.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which is great for you, sure.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:29.080 --> 00:05:31.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you'd likely use me
as a sacrificial pawn.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:33.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footfall]</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:33.830 --> 00:05:35.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll do this myself.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:35.540 --> 00:05:37.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footfall]</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:37.630 --> 00:05:40.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind howling]</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:41.220 --> 00:05:43.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footfall]</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:48.520 --> 00:05:49.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ya see that?</b></Default>

c0000093
00:05:49.600 --> 00:05:52.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We don't trust each other
after that first test.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:52.350 --> 00:05:54.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Safest thing to do
is group up with people</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:54.350 --> 00:05:56.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you already know well.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:56.110 --> 00:05:57.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footfall]</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:59.320 --> 00:06:00.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WIRBEL] Let's go.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:06:00.740 --> 00:06:02.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind howling]</b></Default>

c0000099
00:06:02.150 --> 00:06:04.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EHRE] You could at least
wait for us to get up.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:06:07.160 --> 00:06:08.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000101
00:06:08.240 --> 00:06:10.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] Stubborn fools...</b></Default>

c0000102
00:06:10.120 --> 00:06:11.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why can't they see
that numbers would give us</b></Default>

c0000103
00:06:11.960 --> 00:06:13.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>an advantage this time?</b></Default>

c0000104
00:06:14.620 --> 00:06:16.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should go, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:06:16.790 --> 00:06:19.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, of course, if you're sure.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:06:19.340 --> 00:06:22.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everyone's made their choice,
they know who they trust.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:06:22.800 --> 00:06:25.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footfall]</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:28.470 --> 00:06:29.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Interesting.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:06:31.390 --> 00:06:33.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I believe I'll accompany
the two of you inside.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:35.230 --> 00:06:37.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE] You seem like
you'll have an easier time</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:37.650 --> 00:06:39.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than the rest of the mages.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:42.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Just don't get in the way.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:42.610 --> 00:06:46.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE] I shall neither
interfere nor offer you aid.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:06:48.160 --> 00:06:49.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footfall]</b></Default>

c0000115
00:06:53.790 --> 00:06:55.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] This is the best
route for us to follow.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:06:55.540 --> 00:06:57.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000117
00:06:58.670 --> 00:06:59.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Proceed with caution,</b></Default>

c0000118
00:06:59.920 --> 00:07:01.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we'll map
the labyrinth as we go.</b></Default>

c0000119
00:07:01.590 --> 00:07:03.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000120
00:07:12.180 --> 00:07:14.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footfall]</b></Default>

c0000121
00:07:14.230 --> 00:07:16.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] That stone's a trap.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:07:16.150 --> 00:07:18.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please try to be more careful.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:07:18.480 --> 00:07:19.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000124
00:07:21.940 --> 00:07:24.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000125
00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:27.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] You have such extensive
knowledge of dungeons.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:07:27.450 --> 00:07:28.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Perhaps...</b></Default>

c0000127
00:07:28.570 --> 00:07:30.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>though, that wasn't
always the case.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:07:30.200 --> 00:07:31.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footfall]</b></Default>

c0000129
00:07:31.790 --> 00:07:33.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himmel actually loved
to explore them.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:07:34.910 --> 00:07:36.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He made us trudge through
so many of them</b></Default>

c0000131
00:07:36.710 --> 00:07:38.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>while we were hunting monsters.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:07:39.500 --> 00:07:41.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himmel loved dungeons?</b></Default>

c0000133
00:07:41.250 --> 00:07:42.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you mean by that?</b></Default>

c0000134
00:07:43.420 --> 00:07:44.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Exactly what it sounds like.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:07:45.670 --> 00:07:46.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
He said they excited him.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:07:48.010 --> 00:07:49.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kind of absurd, isn't it?</b></Default>

c0000137
00:07:49.640 --> 00:07:51.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footfall]</b></Default>

c0000138
00:07:51.220 --> 00:07:53.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000139
00:07:53.970 --> 00:07:56.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] These stairs should
take us down to the next floor.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:07:56.520 --> 00:07:58.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000141
00:07:58.560 --> 00:07:59.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] Yes, you're right,</b></Default>

c0000142
00:07:59.810 --> 00:08:01.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>which is why
we're turning around.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:08:02.520 --> 00:08:04.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's more
of this level to explore.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:08:04.690 --> 00:08:06.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER] A smart decision.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:08:06.150 --> 00:08:07.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000146
00:08:07.530 --> 00:08:09.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] I'm confused.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:08:09.160 --> 00:08:11.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're here to slay the monster
lurking in the basement levels.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:08:12.910 --> 00:08:14.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Haven't you learned
anything in our travels?</b></Default>

c0000149
00:08:16.790 --> 00:08:19.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In a dungeon, it's important
to explore the entire area</b></Default>

c0000150
00:08:19.580 --> 00:08:21.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before proceeding
to the next floor.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:08:21.880 --> 00:08:23.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Every adventurer knows that.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:08:23.750 --> 00:08:25.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
I've never heard it before.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:08:27.130 --> 00:08:28.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] You find that
ridiculous, don't you?</b></Default>

c0000154
00:08:29.930 --> 00:08:31.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000155
00:08:31.720 --> 00:08:34.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Think of it as us having
a good time together</b></Default>

c0000156
00:08:34.100 --> 00:08:35.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>while helping people.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:08:36.060 --> 00:08:38.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
It won't always be that simple.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:08:38.440 --> 00:08:40.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The further we travel,
the more dangerous</b></Default>

c0000159
00:08:40.190 --> 00:08:41.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the dungeons will become.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:42.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] A good point.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:08:43.520 --> 00:08:45.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
I'll still have fun even then.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:08:46.030 --> 00:08:47.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll relish
